        <updateDate>2008-11-17T17:50:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends federal veterans law to authorize the Secretary of Veterans Affairs, subject to the availability of appropriations, to increase by up to $1,000 a month the rate of the Medal of Honor special pension.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>81</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-09-24</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Passed House without amendment</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-11-17T17:49:22Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary has been expanded because action occurred on the measure.)</b></p> <p>Amends federal veterans law to authorize the Secretary of Veterans Affairs, subject to the availability of appropriations, to increase by up to $1,000 a month the rate of the Medal of Honor special pension.</p> <p>Terminates such authority at the end of FY2013.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
